try not to foget 
opacity: 1; to opacity: 0; from not seethrouh to completly seethrough
all of its child elements inherit the same transparency

auto - the browser calculates the margin
length - specifies a margin in px, pt, cm, etc.
% - specifies a margin in % of the width of the containing element
inherit - specifies that the margin should be inherited from the parent element

If I wanted to include the padding and border amounts in the total width of the element
box-sizing: border-box

